        {
            "id": 6169309,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 上緯投控(3708)急拉3.31%報125.5元，成交8,557張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>上緯投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3708:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3708\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3708-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.31%，26日12:34報125.5元，成交8,557張，今日跌幅為4.56％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>上緯投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3708:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3708\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3708-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲14.85%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-246 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-530 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+284 張</li> <li>融資增減：+921 張</li> <li>融券增減：+213 張</li> </ul></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6169309",
